Join the Quilluminati (Brian, John, Mike, and Philip) as we discuss Robert E. Howard's Conan the Conqueror, also titled Hour of the Dragon, the only novel-length Conan story that Howard wrote. We will start spoiler-free and announce the next Quilluminati read before moving on to spoilers. 
