Starting out spoiler free, Big Al, Trevor (a.k.a. my best friend from high school), Daniel and I have a chat about The Edan Trilogy! We begin with spoiler-free questions and observations from each participant and move on to spoilers for each of the books in turn (The Way of Edan, The Prophet of Edan, and Return to Edan).
